Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.59,0:00:13.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Cherry...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:14.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.89,0:00:17.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:20.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:28.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's coming over today...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.58,0:00:30.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So be a good girl, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.25,0:01:36.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:37.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.98,0:01:45.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.43,0:01:47.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I baked some cookies yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:49.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd bring some over for you to try, Minami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:52.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Cherry-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:01:54.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to try some too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.07,0:02:04.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Cherry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.58,0:02:05.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.63,0:02:10.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, dogs sometimes tend to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.57,0:02:12.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:15.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Would it be alright if I gave her a cookie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.65,0:02:17.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.39,0:02:19.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she would be happy to have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:22.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:39.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She went to bury it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.03,0:02:41.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't eat it, did she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.13,0:02:48.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's Cherry-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.59,0:02:51.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Her nose is all black!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.72,0:02:57.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, that's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.41,0:02:59.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:01.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My cell phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.59,0:03:02.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cherry-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.63,0:03:04.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't bury it, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:05.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:07.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep on looking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:08.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:15.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure have a dirty face...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.30,0:03:17.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You always seem to have it easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.77,0:03:20.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Tsukasa loses her phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:21.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata is way late...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.99,0:03:23.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't even bother to call us, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.42,0:03:25.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:30.75,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,No, because I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:33.56,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,A Scorpio woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:35.80,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll laugh heartily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:38.85,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I'm satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:41.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:43.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Cherry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:53.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your paws are so hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:55.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not comforting at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:59.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,These paws aren't squishy like they are in manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:01.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I am in despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:06.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No reaction whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:09.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cherry, stupid dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:12.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There are times when even if call her, she won't wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.57,0:04:14.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, she's not stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.05,0:04:18.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cherry, you stupid dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:20.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cherry, you lazy bum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:22.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lazy bum?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:23.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cherry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:25.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You fat dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.48,0:04:27.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Drooling dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:29.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.36,0:04:30.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lazy bum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:34.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:37.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,At least she's aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:39.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A stupid dog like yourself that sleeps all day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:41.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...deserves to be called a lazy bum!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:44.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I try, no matter what I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:46.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...she never wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:50.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, she's sleeping right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.01,0:04:56.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:57.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.54,0:05:03.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.81,0:05:05.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:09.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a cute and quiet dog, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:11.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:19.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cherry-chan, you're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.72,0:05:22.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cherry-chan, you're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:23.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.74,0:05:27.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Cherry-chan was being so quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:28.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so, I couldn't resist...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:31.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But to have a huge dog like this lying in the hallway...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:33.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This house sure is laid-back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:35.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she's so quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.41,0:05:37.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just looking at her makes me feel at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:40.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a dog at home too, so I totally know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:42.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, didn't you need to use the restroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:44.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:48.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:54.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:56.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What-!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.45,0:05:58.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so quiet around the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:06:00.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you suddenly reacting to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:06.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:07.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:09.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good girl today, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:12.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, shake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.65,0:06:18.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not gonna do it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:21.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Minami-chan's dog, so I thought you would be a bit smarter...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:23.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:27.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.09,0:06:27.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit, girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:28.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:31.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What an honest dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:34.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.17,0:06:34.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:36.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:37.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lay off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:39.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:41.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:50.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand big dogs at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:51.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What the-!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:53.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:56.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Minami, dinner time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:02.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, Cherry's not eating her dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:04.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.01,0:07:07.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I even put in some of the canned food you got for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:08.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But she still won't eat it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:11.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she liked that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:26.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cherry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.86,0:07:28.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:29.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:32.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:34.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you digging up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:36.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:37.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You were eating the stuff you buried?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:40.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.57,0:07:42.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're happy, Cherry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:43.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.52,0:07:57.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, that was pretty sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:08:01.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you start playing online games, Hiiragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.47,0:08:02.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.32,0:08:03.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, believe it or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.68,0:08:08.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami is a big fan of the artist who worked on the anime adaptation for this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:10.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:13.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've finally given into the dark side, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:15.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:17.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say unnecessary things!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:18.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:22.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you want to copy the anime, then aren't the Hiiragi sisters a mis-casting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.84,0:08:23.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be the reverse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:24.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.34,0:08:25.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:28.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami, thx!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:30.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:37.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:39.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of our own survival...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:40.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...swapping them would be a fatal mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.88,0:08:42.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see what you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:45.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a lot safer this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:46.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Konata...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:48.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling the jobs we have in the game...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:51.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the ones that are in the anime are different...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:53.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, those are higher level jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:57.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to transfer professions from our current jobs to get those done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:08:59.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you switch jobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:00.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:01.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:03.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.22,0:09:05.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They claim that the anime and game will progress concurrently...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.22,0:09:08.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but once the anime finishes airing, it's all "coming soon."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:12.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But when you're in a game world like this, you start getting immersed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:15.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And you really do get reminded of those game-based anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:19.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, like the one they set up to look like an online game but was actually offline.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:22.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why they didn't release that online.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.18,0:09:27.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I honestly believed that it was an online game, and I went looking for it all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:30.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That does seem to happen often.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:36.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa, just hit ENTER.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:37.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:40.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aah, aah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:43.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, I can finally talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:46.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering why you weren't talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:49.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't hit ENTER, you won't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:53.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it's so nice forming parties with people you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:54.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:58.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick-up groups are hit or miss, so it's a gamble every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:10:00.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you guys usually do, Kona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:03.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just start spamming for groups or form one myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:06.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, there are lots of times when no one picks me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:10.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you miss the prime time for groups, then you end up playing solo the whole night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:12.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause no one ever wants to be the party leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:14.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And everyone just looks for groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:17.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention there are lots of times where you get too many of the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.46,0:10:22.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you form a group in a rush, you could end up wasting even more time wiping.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:25.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I have absolutely no idea what you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:35.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa, your spells never do much damage, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:36.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.77,0:10:40.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mages are supposed to be strong enough to solo-farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:42.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you putting your stats?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:43.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stats?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:46.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.48,0:10:48.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But normally in games...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:52.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...when you level up, you just automatically learn spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:53.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I thought this was just like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:55.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.54,0:10:58.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.31,0:11:01.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I'm level 10, I can attack twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:06.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If I keep leveling up, I wonder if I can pull off three attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:08.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:11.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this feeling of déjà vu...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:15.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels very much like I'm playing a Lodoss tabletalk RPG...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:16.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,More nonsense...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:20.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This game's got a lot of emotes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:24.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, we should make a victory pose for our party!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:29.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that really necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:32.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes it was, Kagami. Especially since we're online.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:35.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This floor has 3 enemies and a hidden treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:41.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,For this boss, I'll pull him away and kite him, so you guys DPS him from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:43.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's weak to fire, so make sure you take advantage of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:47.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you talk to that guy over there, he'll give you a quest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:51.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, you just talk to the old man by the exit and you'll get some cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:53.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kona-chan, you know so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:57.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, all that information is floating around the net.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:12:02.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some amazing sites that'll have a complete walkthrough uploaded the same day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:04.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost as though they're getting paid for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.77,0:12:07.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If only they could redirect all that energy into fueling society...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:09.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and make themselves useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.24,0:12:15.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is invincible Pizza-La Shield, there's nothing to fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:17.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pizza-La?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:19.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an in-game promotional item.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:23.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you order a pizza, you can get such special items.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:26.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I feel like you're falling into their trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:26.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:29.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm aware of it, I still do it for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:31.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You too!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:32.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:33.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:35.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to the hot springs as a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:39.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I don't think we'll be on during Golden Week.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:43.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm going somewhere with Yu-chan, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:45.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it won't be too crowded...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:47.28,ls_oldfilm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz270\pos(766,162)\be1}After Golden Week
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.05,0:12:53.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:55.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:02.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, what did this kid do after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:03.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the right answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:04.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:06.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mayumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:10.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we're off to go see the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:12.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch over the house, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:13.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:15.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami, you're really not going to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.93,0:13:18.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's too much trouble anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:19.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:20.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to miss out on this chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:24.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to get a bit nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:27.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa, why don't you try participating?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.02,0:13:27.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:30.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:32.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:33.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure to lock up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:34.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:35.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:40.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, this wife is pretty scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.24,0:13:41.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:42.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like this is normal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:44.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't think so at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:47.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall make that wish of yours come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.63,0:13:50.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:52.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And what's with that getup?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.07,0:13:53.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:56.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, my current designation is a mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:58.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "designation?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.51,0:14:00.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:04.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your evil stepmother and sisters are picking on you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:05.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:06.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:07.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to go to the ball too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:08.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I said nothing of the sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:14.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the fairy godmother, and I'm Cinderella...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:18.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and now I must get on a carriage and go attend the ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.57,0:14:19.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:21.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:25.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not even a carriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.10,0:14:28.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about the details, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:31.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's head out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:32.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami, you get on as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:33.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.63,0:14:34.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.27,0:14:35.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you {\i1}really{\i0} want to have a carriage that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:36.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:39.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know what the hell you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:42.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I never intended to go to the ball in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.43,0:14:43.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.81,0:14:45.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like you know it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:46.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:48.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:49.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,For sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:50.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,For sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:51.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:52.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:01.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.14,0:15:02.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What was she thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:03.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:05.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to have her turn that back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:06.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:07.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A-An earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:11.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:14.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:15.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:18.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't go outside right now if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.57,0:15:19.40,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.40,0:15:20.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:21.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:24.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you refused to leave the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.87,0:15:26.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that I don't want to go, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:29.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll just go to the dance hall like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.06,0:15:33.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.25,0:15:34.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go, now stop all of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:39.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you looking forward to the ball, Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:40.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:42.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet the truth is that you're really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:44.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You tsundere, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:44.07,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop calling me a tsundere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.07,0:15:46.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, why is a fairy godmother such as yourself coming along too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:47.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:50.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We should take this opportunity to get you all dressed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:52.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you even listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.31,0:15:52.07,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:57.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is the default selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.21,0:15:59.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this isn't something you'd wear to a ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:00.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:04.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're more than qualified for that type of niche, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:04.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:06.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, change my clothes back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:08.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, after I went through all that trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:09.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I never asked you to!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.93,0:16:11.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Change it back right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:12.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:16.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you didn't fix anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:19.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could call this another type of "default".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:21.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, this is your usual cosplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:22.59,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call it cosplay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:28.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody's gonna get hurt real soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:29.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:31.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it right this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:32.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:34.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It fell off...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.27,0:16:35.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.13,0:16:38.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but it looks like I can't change your clothes back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.95,0:16:43.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:46.90,ls_signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H312A47&\3c&H66656C&\bord7\b1\fs60\fnHanoded\pos(658,95)}Fighters' ball in Saitama: {\c&H3B28B1&}Love{\c&H312A47&} is touch and {\c&H3B28B1&}endless{\c&H312A47&}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:51.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How 'bout this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.02,0:16:57.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Winner, Kuroi Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:58.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:03.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I will escape from my life as a bachelorette!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:05.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You just wait for me, Prince Misao!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:06.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:09.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Win, win, and keep on winning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:11.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever wins this competition...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:15.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Will be my bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:18.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're really getting into it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.46,0:17:20.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.19,0:17:22.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hiiragi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:26.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you would come after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.16,0:17:26.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.51,0:17:27.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:27.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:29.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you dress up like this just for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.99,0:17:30.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:33.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiiragi, you're participating too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:33.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.77,0:17:35.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, just participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:38.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fix all your matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:40.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why even have a competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:42.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, I don't want to participate...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:44.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and second, I don't want to become your bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:45.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this, Hiiragi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:47.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being pretty cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:50.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, prince, this is just her "tsun" side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:52.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, which means deep down...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:53.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:54.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:57.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know this was going to happen, which is why I didn't want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.15,0:18:02.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, I'm going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:03.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:05.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:08.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When the clock strikes midnight, all the magic will be undone anyways, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:12.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't leave now, the car will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:13.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How did she know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:15.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares, who cares?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:16.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:17.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for the fight predictions!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:17.60,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a little kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:21.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:23.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The house is still displaced!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:24.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you move it back to its original location?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:28.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I fixed the Starring Inferno, so everything should be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:30.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I not feel reassured?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:31.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:39.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:41.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess time's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.11,0:18:41.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:43.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already past midnight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.59,0:18:44.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.96,0:18:46.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it'll have to stay like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:48.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:50.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you do something with your magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:55.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I was also on the receiving side of a magic spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:57.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why I can't do anything past 12AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:18:59.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean you can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:01.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:04.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered a spell to reset everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:05.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:06.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why didn't you say that earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:10.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well {\i1}you{\i0}  have to say this one, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:12.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then tell me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.84,0:19:14.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:18.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I really have to say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:19.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:20.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really loud, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:21.08,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Really loud!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:21.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:23.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:25.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Things won't return to normal if you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.55,0:19:28.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:33.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ***** with Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.50,0:19:44.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:46.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.42,0:19:47.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:47.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:50.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I should go mail Kona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:52.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tsukasa, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.53,0:19:54.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it totally wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:56.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was against my will...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:19:59.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What I meant is that she totally...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:10.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:20.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:21.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That was amazing, Hiiragi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:23.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just luck, I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:26.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could hit that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:28.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiiragi's little sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:29.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:31.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kusakabe-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.44,0:20:33.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to live in Hiiragi's shadow forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:35.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:37.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No buts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.08,0:20:41.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's your big chance to show your sister up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:45.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Muster up some courage and prove to your sister that you can do it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:47.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:51.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll show 'em the true power of a support character!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:52.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:20:55.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what a nostalgic scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:57.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:01.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:02.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:08.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how it's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:10.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so close...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.98,0:21:12.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, Kusakabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:15.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.23,0:21:18.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Super Ultra Miraculous Eccentric Special...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:20.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Serve!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.28,0:21:21.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,An underhand serve?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.65,0:21:26.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:27.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice receive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:28.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:33.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.62,0:21:34.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.00,0:21:36.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Misakichi, Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:39.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna do a Jet Stream Attack on the attacker!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.17,0:21:39.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:40.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:47.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what's a Jet Stream Attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.60,0:21:49.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, you're not supposed to say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.94,0:21:52.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the plan won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.94,0:21:51.71,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:54.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.67,0:21:58.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.97,0:22:00.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.77,0:22:22.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.99,0:22:28.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Little Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.99,0:22:28.34,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.20,0:22:42.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that is impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.12,0:22:44.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.00,0:22:46.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The tears had fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.12,0:22:47.38,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even when it's tough{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.67,0:22:47.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.66,0:22:48.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.31,0:22:49.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.28,0:22:51.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cutural literacy for the Japanese!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.39,0:22:53.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one that feels that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.21,0:22:55.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Little Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.27,0:22:57.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in sulking there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.32,0:23:00.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna beat down Hiiragi today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.55,0:23:04.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.36,0:23:14.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been relying on Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.83,0:23:19.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.34,0:23:23.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.40,0:23:25.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.04,0:23:27.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do everything I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.90,0:23:38.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.64,0:23:40.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Little Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.54,0:23:44.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guu~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.05,0:23:53.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One more point...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.92,0:23:55.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and our team will...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.52,0:23:56.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...win!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.78,0:23:58.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.87,0:24:01.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't lose, Hiiragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.80,0:24:03.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't let it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.15,0:24:04.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...end like this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.79,0:24:06.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.55,0:24:09.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Spin.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.54,0:24:09.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.74,0:24:12.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just call me the Witch of Kasukabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.45,0:24:14.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.15,0:24:17.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it, Little Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.60,0:24:19.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hit it with everything you got!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.27,0:24:21.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.16,0:24:33.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, it hurts as if I just smacked into something.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.64,0:24:36.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.41,0:24:39.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You really shined today, Hiiragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.28,0:24:40.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.57,0:24:41.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing less from Hiiragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.44,0:24:43.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.91,0:24:45.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.25,0:24:45.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.18,0:24:47.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.67,0:24:49.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose the supporting characters...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.22,0:24:51.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...are never meant to win...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.50,0:24:57.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I still can't match Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.71,0:25:01.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.83,0:25:07.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.32,0:25:14.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven has forsaken us!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.73,0:25:16.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.37,0:25:17.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.15,0:25:18.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just trying to get into the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.21,0:25:20.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.31,0:25:20.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.94,0:25:29.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a story that happened during a summer camping trip for our school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.25,0:25:32.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We had decided to take a hike and were in the midst of our orienteering course.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.87,0:25:35.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's when our group...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.02,0:25:36.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...somehow ended up lost.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.46,0:25:40.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.90,0:25:45.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because {\i1}you{\i0}  forgot the map and compass on the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.62,0:25:48.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, why did we have to go this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.35,0:25:51.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suddenly had the urge to climb a mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.35,0:25:52.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.71,0:25:55.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"Why?" you ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.65,0:25:57.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.73,0:26:00.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now now, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.70,0:26:04.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we start by checking our cell phones?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.64,0:26:08.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, out of range.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.94,0:26:09.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.88,0:26:10.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I got nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.80,0:26:11.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Same.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.95,0:26:14.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we're doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.38,0:26:17.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.84,0:26:21.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We should've been at the camping grounds by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.10,0:26:23.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.36,0:26:27.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the schedule, we were supposed to start making dinner at 5PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.60,0:26:32.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Reacted to the word "dinner", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.49,0:26:35.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, aren't you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.00,0:26:36.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.41,0:26:39.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I ate a ton of these on the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.73,0:26:42.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, again!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.95,0:26:47.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That one was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.30,0:26:50.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, how about we escape absolute starvation with these...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.79,0:26:52.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Starvation seems a bit exaggerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.50,0:26:54.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But these...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.79,0:26:56.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.18,0:26:58.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're one short!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.14,0:27:01.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, may I?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.68,0:27:04.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, there will be six total.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.18,0:27:06.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If we give everyone one piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.43,0:27:09.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,..we can then break the last two into halves again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.82,0:27:10.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.06,0:27:12.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-chan, you're incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.66,0:27:14.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing less from our Miwiki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.89,0:27:18.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh it's nothing, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.49,0:27:21.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we won't have to starve to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.00,0:27:22.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, you're exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.16,0:27:26.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.08,0:27:30.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Izumi-san's words began to seem like less and less of a joke...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.78,0:27:32.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and more of a reality.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.35,0:27:38.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling we're completely and utterly lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.50,0:27:39.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.43,0:27:42.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been walking the same area over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.41,0:27:45.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, if only we had a magnet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.48,0:27:49.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I need to smack you across the face with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.75,0:27:52.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps I should shove it down your throat?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.44,0:27:53.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.50,0:27:55.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami, you're serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.69,0:27:56.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.49,0:28:00.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That looks like the Summer Triangle.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.88,0:28:03.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, I'm pretty sure this direction is East.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.66,0:28:05.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow Tsukasa, that's pretty amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.93,0:28:09.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa, do you like stars that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.64,0:28:12.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, this is the only one I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.35,0:28:16.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the big stars of the Summer Triangle is called Vega...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.45,0:28:18.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it's also the Orihime Boshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.12,0:28:21.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we were born on Tanabata.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.53,0:28:25.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The Big Dipper also looks really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.05,0:28:27.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Kagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.53,0:28:30.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Until the day the Death Omen Star has fallen...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.04,0:28:31.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you must live your life to the fullest!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.92,0:28:34.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, even if we do know the cardinal directions...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.37,0:28:36.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...we still don't know how to get to the camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.94,0:28:39.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And such is our problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.87,0:28:44.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven has forsaken us!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.71,0:28:45.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.56,0:28:49.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,After screaming like that, I'm seriously starting to get hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.98,0:28:53.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And whose fault is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.20,0:28:57.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I never spoke of the idea openly...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.21,0:28:58.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but I was seriously...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.69,0:29:02.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...starting to consider the possibility that we wouldn't make it back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.14,0:29:05.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not descending...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.65,0:29:06.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.99,0:29:08.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We've walked quite a bit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.28,0:29:10.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.96,0:29:15.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we lost our sense of direction inside the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.12,0:29:16.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.14,0:29:18.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Story number ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.46,0:29:20.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In the silent forest...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.97,0:29:24.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you could hear the *pant* *pant* of their breathing...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.96,0:29:26.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.34,0:29:28.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The Gathering of One Hundred Supernatural Tales.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.23,0:29:30.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you tell a hundred ghost stores in a single night...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.59,0:29:33.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...a real ghost will descend upon you!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.23,0:29:33.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.34,0:29:35.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.72,0:29:38.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you can feel a cold sensation on your cheek...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.22,0:29:42.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.60,0:29:43.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.28,0:29:46.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...a campout at night means ghost stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.43,0:29:48.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And after, love stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.68,0:29:49.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.87,0:29:52.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Did I say something weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.68,0:29:54.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Story number eighteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.97,0:29:57.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried calling out, "Hey!"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.92,0:29:59.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But there was only silence...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.90,0:30:01.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...then all of a sudden-
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.95,0:30:06.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that supposed to be the sound of you blowing out a candle?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.48,0:30:06.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.43,0:30:09.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In The Gathering of One Hundred Supernatural Tales...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.11,0:30:11.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you're supposed to blow out a candle...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.11,0:30:14.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...each time you finish a story, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.50,0:30:16.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Miwiki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.84,0:30:17.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.66,0:30:19.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.40,0:30:20.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What story was I on again?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.00,0:30:23.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Story number sixteen, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.75,0:30:23.75,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going backwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.04,0:30:31.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Sazae-
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.95,0:30:32.28,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you mean Izumi!?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.28,0:30:34.28,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell are you guys right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.49,0:30:40.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you guys have {\i1}any{\i0}  idea how worried we all were?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.93,0:30:44.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What awaited our return to the camping grounds...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.02,0:30:46.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...were Kuroi-sensei's harsh words.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.73,0:30:47.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.82,0:30:49.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you must be {\i1}extra{\i0}  careful from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.04,0:30:51.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.42,0:30:56.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hungry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.62,0:31:07.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.40,0:31:09.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.26,0:31:10.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.12,0:31:12.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Indeed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.59,0:31:17.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the curry we had that day was truly delicious.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.57,0:31:20.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Perhaps, it was even the most delicious curry I had ever had.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.92,0:31:25.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And so something outrageous like that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.45,0:31:28.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a really troublesome day.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.09,0:31:30.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.00,0:31:33.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you seemed to be enjoying yourself while you were telling the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.06,0:31:34.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.36,0:31:35.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.23,0:31:36.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Very much so.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.44,0:31:47.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.54,0:31:48.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.84,0:31:56.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.26,0:31:59.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a place I want to stop by on the way back...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.27,0:32:01.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going {\i1}straight{\i0}  home with no detours.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.69,0:32:03.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.46,0:32:04.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't take long at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.88,0:32:05.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.66,0:32:07.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.18,0:32:08.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.02,0:32:10.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say such harsh words...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.84,0:32:12.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Gah, get off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.44,0:32:13.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.82,0:32:15.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But just for a little bit, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.93,0:32:17.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.49,0:32:19.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a nice person, Kagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.00,0:32:20.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going straight home afterwards, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.52,0:32:21.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.05,0:32:23.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Kona-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.30,0:32:24.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we stopping at?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.05,0:32:26.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.26,0:32:28.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Some pet show that just recently opened up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.17,0:32:28.67,ls_oldfilm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fs70\pos(758,478)}Pet Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.99,0:32:30.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a pet shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.09,0:32:32.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How nostalgic!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.09,0:32:39.97,ls_signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HC0E3ED&\3c&H999F6C&\fnBig Bimbo NC\fs60\blur1\pos(690,74)}Minoru~pa~
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.62,0:32:34.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to buy a dog or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.42,0:32:37.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to look at the bunnies.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.08,0:32:39.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see the cute puppies.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.24,0:32:39.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.26,0:32:41.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This{\i0}  is what I wanted to look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.99,0:32:44.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this cat has really nice fur.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.00,0:32:47.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata, I'll remind you right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.56,0:32:49.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...this cat isn't a witch or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.31,0:32:50.57,ls_oldfilm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(145,480)\blur2\c&HB8C0C3&}This cat isn't a witch\Nor anything, so don't\Nbother it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.75,0:32:52.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.74,0:32:54.24,ls_oldfilm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\pos(173,92)}I know that. I won't go as far as collecting its soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.16,0:32:54.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go as far as collecting its soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.91,0:32:56.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you've said up until now...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.18,0:32:58.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.83,0:33:00.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I have returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.33,0:33:00.70,ls_oldfilm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(720,429)\fs60\blur2}I have returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.58,0:33:03.91,ls_oldfilm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(297,90)\blur2}I will use you up like a ragged cloth!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.95,0:33:03.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I will use you up like a ragged cloth!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.21,0:33:06.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this cat must have really nice lineage.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.83,0:33:09.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-chan, you come from a really nice lineage as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.54,0:33:10.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.48,0:33:12.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you're using that in the right context.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.79,0:33:13.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.79,0:33:16.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, Miyuki-san is the Galactic Fairy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.47,0:33:16.47,ls_oldfilm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz270\pos(760,187)\blur2}The Galactic Fairy
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.47,0:33:18.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Although her appearance is slightly different...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.17,0:33:21.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the most famous frogs in Pekopon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.30,0:33:24.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ge~ro Gero Gero
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.28,0:33:25.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta~ma Tama Tama
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.33,0:33:26.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ge~ro Gero Gero!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.28,0:33:27.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta~ma Tama Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.94,0:33:30.69,ls_oldfilm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz270\pos(858,210)\fnArial Black\blur2}Ge-ro Gero Gero
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.94,0:33:30.69,ls_oldfilm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz270\fnArial Black\blur2\pos(489,178)}Ta-ma Tama Tama
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.16,0:33:28.52,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Ge~ro Gero Gero!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.11,0:33:29.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta~ma Tama Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.83,0:33:50.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.63,0:33:53.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a dark-spotted frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.08,0:33:56.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I look like a Japanese tree frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.68,0:33:58.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I seem to be a bullfrog.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.84,0:33:59.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a common toad...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.92,0:34:00.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.93,0:34:02.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.79,0:34:04.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.18,0:34:08.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.40,0:34:13.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Alrighty then!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.51,0:34:18.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,For-For-For-Forgot my something...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.52,0:34:29.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.11,0:34:30.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.05,0:34:31.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Legendary Girl A!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.20,0:34:33.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This means...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.77,0:34:38.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I must have her buy something!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.12,0:34:44.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold! The best armament I have collected!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.72,0:34:46.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,With these slick deals...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.14,0:34:49.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even Legendary Girl A can resist!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.37,0:34:59.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! She's AFK?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.18,0:35:11.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.93,0:35:14.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's this era's super...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.06,0:35:17.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...super idol, Akira Kogami here!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.96,0:35:20.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.94,0:35:21.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.79,0:35:25.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And...!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.02,0:35:32.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Her assistant, Minoru Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.83,0:35:34.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Moving on!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.74,0:35:34.27,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.74,0:35:38.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, if he hears you call out for him, I think he'll show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.82,0:35:40.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're really quiet, he might now hear you...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.91,0:35:43.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So please, say it as quietly as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.63,0:35:43.30,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.13,0:35:45.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, one , two...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.46,0:35:48.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Minoru-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.12,0:35:52.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wa-wa-wa-wa-wa-wa!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.69,0:35:54.43,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you've appeared after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.71,0:35:54.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wa-wa-wa-wa-wa-wa...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.13,0:35:55.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wa~
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.98,0:36:00.68,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to show up...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.76,0:35:59.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wa-wa-wa-wa-waa...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.97,0:36:04.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wa-wa-wa-wa-wa-wa-wa-wa-waaaa...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.06,0:36:05.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wa-waah...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.77,0:36:08.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! I'm the assistant, Minoru Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.57,0:36:09.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not gonna do a little skit for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.11,0:36:10.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A skit?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.84,0:36:11.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.66,0:36:14.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you would stop in front of the camera...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.66,0:36:12.28,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.02,0:36:17.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And then you would say, "And now I'll put on a little performance..."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.02,0:36:14.32,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.24,0:36:20.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.40,0:36:21.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.95,0:36:27.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.04,0:36:30.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's 10 years worth of experience for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.56,0:36:34.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.57,0:36:34.45,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.45,0:36:35.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, nice to meet you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.95,0:36:37.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.57,0:36:37.95,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.96,0:36:39.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.06,0:36:40.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.79,0:36:42.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something that's pretty popular around these parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.66,0:36:43.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nezumi-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.89,0:36:44.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.57,0:36:45.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, it's totally in style.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.84,0:36:46.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear it's the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.96,0:36:47.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.57,0:36:48.32,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.64,0:36:49.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.65,0:36:49.41,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even care?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.61,0:36:50.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, what is it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.71,0:36:52.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm referring to is this entire situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.31,0:36:54.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.66,0:36:55.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.61,0:36:56.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with what?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.91,0:36:57.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's a live-action filming.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.70,0:36:58.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A live...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.21,0:37:00.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A live Lucky Channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.01,0:37:02.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.80,0:37:05.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so loud!!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.08,0:37:06.09,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.09,0:37:07.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's calm down, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.80,0:37:08.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, c'mon...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.75,0:37:10.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this lovely?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.92,0:37:12.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.85,0:37:13.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.85,0:37:16.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that teary-eyed face?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.35,0:37:18.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, this is an animation!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.43,0:37:20.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but there was an animation.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.60,0:37:21.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just before this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.82,0:37:23.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.47,0:37:26.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.86,0:37:28.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Akira Kogami?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.04,0:37:28.46,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.46,0:37:29.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me repeat myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.32,0:37:29.78,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.78,0:37:30.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm this era's...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.73,0:37:31.14,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.94,0:37:31.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This era's...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.94,0:37:33.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Super idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.83,0:37:34.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.39,0:37:35.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.49,0:37:37.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.81,0:37:40.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...we had you do this live performance that one one else could pull off.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.62,0:37:41.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.53,0:37:43.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's a visual animation.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.25,0:37:44.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So we need to have some animations...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.46,0:37:45.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and also some visuals...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.43,0:37:47.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.66,0:37:47.08,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.02,0:37:49.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,By having both parts separate and then together...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.59,0:37:51.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...it'll be twice as good.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.33,0:37:51.17,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I just realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.48,0:37:52.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.04,0:37:53.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit like...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.54,0:37:53.99,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,And Original...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.45,0:37:53.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.26,0:37:56.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...Visual...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.84,0:37:57.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Animation?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.50,0:37:58.17,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Animation?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.17,0:37:58.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.97,0:38:01.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Minoru Shiraishi is an original...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.00,0:38:00.42,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.87,0:38:03.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the visual...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.28,0:38:04.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...as well as the animation?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.34,0:38:06.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That means the entire program is about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.12,0:38:06.55,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.55,0:38:07.64,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.03,0:38:08.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.64,0:38:08.92,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,You have it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.07,0:38:10.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Akira is supposed to be the super idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.84,0:38:10.78,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,You're absolutely correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.15,0:38:11.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are all the staff...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.37,0:38:12.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...on Minoru-kun's...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.08,0:38:14.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.81,0:38:13.19,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.19,0:38:14.76,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.76,0:38:16.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's not enough love!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.96,0:38:16.86,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.86,0:38:17.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I am shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.08,0:38:18.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shocked?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.65,0:38:30.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um..
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.54,0:38:30.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.68,0:38:32.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.19,0:38:33.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's playing...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.01,0:38:34.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.50,0:38:36.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, the theme song...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.73,0:38:37.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.23,0:38:38.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.83,0:38:40.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh this... this is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.13,0:38:42.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll disappear over here, so don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.09,0:38:45.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The staff, everyone, loves you...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.63,0:38:46.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Akira-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.47,0:38:46.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.28,0:38:47.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.93,0:38:48.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.80,0:38:49.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Could we get some water or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.64,0:38:50.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.99,0:38:52.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Staff, may I have some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.21,0:38:52.71,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.71,0:38:54.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Some water, please... ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.49,0:38:55.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.24,0:38:56.49,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.96,0:38:57.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, please rest a little, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.04,0:38:59.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.26,0:39:01.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.45,0:39:02.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.44,0:39:03.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.89,0:39:04.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.58,0:39:07.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I was saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.78,0:39:09.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, I'm a little thirsty, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.53,0:39:11.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.85,0:39:12.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.41,0:39:13.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Staff!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.02,0:39:14.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Staff!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.15,0:39:16.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, could I also...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.62,0:39:17.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...get some water here?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.15,0:39:19.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Staff!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.79,0:39:20.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Staff!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.13,0:39:21.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.07,0:39:23.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like some water...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.53,0:39:24.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.14,0:39:25.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you taking the mic?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.49,0:39:28.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh, that's a bit strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.25,0:39:28.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.97,0:39:29.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's my water?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.77,0:39:30.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My water...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.42,0:39:30.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Staff~
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.64,0:39:39.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.45,0:39:41.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.69,0:39:43.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.44,0:39:46.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.97,0:39:48.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.52,0:39:50.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.98,0:39:52.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,While this certainly is water...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.13,0:39:54.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not quite what I was expecting...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.27,0:39:55.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.39,0:39:58.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.62,0:40:00.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.15,0:40:15.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.54,0:40:16.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.66,0:40:16.68,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.87,0:40:19.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.04,0:40:19.35,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.66,0:40:23.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.07,0:40:23.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.11,0:40:24.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.97,0:40:25.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.47,0:40:27.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.52,0:40:27.72,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.72,0:40:29.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.09,0:40:33.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They kept on telling me, "You'll be in the main series."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.89,0:40:33.25,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.25,0:40:35.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But those were all empty promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.31,0:40:37.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So then I tried being a pop star...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.35,0:40:38.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but that didn't last long, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.60,0:40:38.83,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.83,0:40:39.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.42,0:40:46.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I even told them that I was willing to play some side parts and the like in the main series, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.57,0:40:46.87,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.57,0:40:47.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But here I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.50,0:40:49.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine, Akira-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.51,0:40:49.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll see!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.99,0:40:50.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good things will happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.97,0:40:51.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But they haven't...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.96,0:40:53.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not matter what I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.11,0:40:55.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like there's just not enough love in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.28,0:40:55.50,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.50,0:40:56.41,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-sama, the ending...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.12,0:40:58.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ehh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.77,0:41:00.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end already?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.45,0:41:02.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira's so lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.35,0:41:04.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.80,0:41:05.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And then this!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.76,0:41:08.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is new.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.34,0:41:09.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.00,0:41:09.72,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Right around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.63,0:41:10.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.36,0:41:11.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.76,0:41:15.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please send all your love to Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.82,0:41:15.47,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.14,0:41:14.51,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.79,0:41:16.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And thus...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.73,0:41:17.08,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.91,0:41:20.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I await the next time we can see each other again!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.85,0:41:24.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But for now, bye-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.85,0:41:24.92,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bee!!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.52,0:41:27.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm seriously going to do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.46,0:41:28.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.78,0:41:30.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As high as the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.50,0:41:31.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.00,0:41:31.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
