Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.40,0:41:32.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.16,0:41:33.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.97,0:41:34.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.64,0:41:35.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.59,0:41:36.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.79,0:41:37.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.28,0:41:37.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.67,0:41:39.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to aim for the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.32,0:41:39.52,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.52,0:41:40.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere so high you can't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.54,0:41:41.22,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.62,0:41:42.26,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,You're approaching it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.49,0:41:42.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.67,0:41:43.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly but surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.34,0:41:43.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.49,0:41:44.52,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Inching your way to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.78,0:41:45.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.26,0:41:46.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, it makes me think I should climb to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.05,0:41:46.95,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.46,0:41:48.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.44,0:41:50.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The both of us climbing to the top...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.91,0:41:50.66,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoom!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.22,0:41:51.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoom!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.99,0:41:54.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it. Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.80,0:41:55.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll figure it out just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.89,0:41:56.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.95,0:41:58.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll be at the top just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.67,0:42:01.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems unreliable, but I'll give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.11,0:42:01.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.80,0:38:26.61,ls_end_special,,0000,0000,0000,,YOU are SHOCK!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.61,0:38:30.02,ls_end_special,,0000,0000,0000,,The skies have fallen from love.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.01,0:38:32.80,ls_end_special,,0000,0000,0000,,YOU are SHOCK!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.80,0:38:36.41,ls_end_special,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart has fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.03,0:38:40.47,ls_end_special,,0000,0000,0000,,Even bound by chains, the heart burns.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.47,0:38:43.48,ls_end_special,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.48,0:38:49.64,ls_end_special,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who interfere will be taken down by a single finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.64,0:38:51.59,ls_end_special,,0000,0000,0000,,YOU are SHOCK!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.59,0:38:55.48,ls_end_special,,0000,0000,0000,,The pulse quickens from love.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.96,0:38:57.81,ls_end_special,,0000,0000,0000,,YOU are SHOCK!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.81,0:39:01.38,ls_end_special,,0000,0000,0000,,My pulse quickens.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.23,0:39:05.37,ls_end_special,,0000,0000,0000,,Searching for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.37,0:39:08.27,ls_end_special,,0000,0000,0000,,My wandering heart is now burning up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.27,0:39:15.04,ls_end_special,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything must dissolve and scatter apart tragically.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.18,0:39:19.24,ls_end_special,,0000,0000,0000,,To protect our love,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.24,0:39:22.28,ls_end_special,,0000,0000,0000,,You departed on a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.28,0:39:28.49,ls_end_special,,0000,0000,0000,,Had lost sight of tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.49,0:39:31.67,ls_end_special,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.67,0:39:35.09,ls_end_special,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a face that has forgotten how to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.09,0:39:40.58,ls_end_special,,0000,0000,0000,,Reclaim the love!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.69,0:39:43.88,ls_end_special,,0000,0000,0000,,You are already dead!
